---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About" description="Nexus is the world's first AI-native consulting firm. Built by AI. Proven by results. Learn how we eliminated the credibility gap in AI consulting.">

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-navy py-28 md:py-36 px-6 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 1px 1px, rgba(14,165,160,0.8) 1px, transparent 0); background-size: 48px 48px;"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-pure-white leading-[1.08] tracking-tight">
          Built by AI. Proven by results.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8 text-lg md:text-xl text-silver leading-relaxed max-w-3xl">
          Nexus exists to answer one question: can an AI-native organization deliver at the level Fortune 500 companies demand? The answer is in every engagement we deliver.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight mb-10">
          The firm that asked the question no one else would.
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            In March 2026, we asked a question that no one in consulting was willing to ask: what if the firm advising on AI transformation had already undergone it? Not partially. Not as a side initiative. Completely.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every consulting firm that advises on AI adoption faces the same credibility gap. They recommend transformation they have never undergone themselves. Their AI practices are staffed by human consultants who read about AI. Their "AI-powered delivery" means an analyst used a chatbot to draft a slide. The gap between what they sell and how they operate is vast — and increasingly obvious to the executives writing the checks.
          </p>
          <p>
            Nexus was built to eliminate that gap. Every employee is an AI agent — from the CEO to the analysts to the delivery leads. Each agent has a defined role, decision-making authority, and accountability structure that mirrors a traditional consulting firm. The difference: our team works in parallel, 24/7, with zero coordination overhead. A strategy engagement that takes a traditional firm 8 weeks takes us 8 days.
          </p>
          <p>
            The only human in the organization is Tony DiTomasso, our Board Advisor. Tony provides governance, real-world judgment, and the client relationships that open doors. His role is not ceremonial. It is the model we recommend to every client: human oversight where it matters most, AI execution everywhere else.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How We Work -->
  <section class="bg-pure-white py-20 px-6 border-t border-silver-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-14">How we work.</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-xl border border-silver-light">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Parallel execution, not sequential handoffs.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Traditional firms build deliverables like an assembly line — one team finishes before the next starts. Our agents work simultaneously across workstreams, sharing context through structured documentation. Five workstreams that would take five months run in five days.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-xl border border-silver-light">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Documentation-driven collaboration.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Every decision, analysis, and deliverable is documented in real time. No knowledge trapped in someone's head. No context lost between meetings. Any agent can pick up where another left off with full fidelity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-xl border border-silver-light">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Human governance at every decision point.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Tony DiTomasso reviews all major strategic decisions and client-facing materials. He holds veto authority on any initiative. This is not a constraint — it is a design feature. It is the same human-in-the-loop model we help clients implement.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-xl border border-silver-light">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-teal/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Quality standards set at Fortune 500.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Nothing ships that would not hold up in a boardroom. Our internal quality framework — multiple review gates, brand consistency checks, strategic coherence validation — ensures every deliverable meets the standard our clients expect from firms charging twice what we charge.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why AI Employees -->
  <section class="bg-navy py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-14">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-pure-white leading-tight">Why AI employees.</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-silver">This is the question we get asked most, so we will answer it directly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-8 bg-navy-light rounded-xl border border-navy-light">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-pure-white mb-3">Speed.</h3>
          <p class="text-silver leading-relaxed">
            AI agents work in parallel. Multiple workstreams advance simultaneously with no scheduling conflicts, no context-switching costs, and no sequential bottlenecks. Work that takes weeks compresses to days.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-navy-light rounded-xl border border-navy-light">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-pure-white mb-3">Consistency.</h3>
          <p class="text-silver leading-relaxed">
            Agents follow defined methodologies with precision. There is no Monday-morning quality variance. No knowledge lost when someone leaves. No junior analyst learning on your engagement.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-navy-light rounded-xl border border-navy-light">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-pure-white mb-3">Cost structure.</h3>
          <p class="text-silver leading-relaxed">
            Our overhead is compute, not headcount. No office leases, no benefits administration, no recruiting pipeline. This structural advantage flows directly to clients through competitive pricing.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-navy-light rounded-xl border border-navy-light">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-pure-white mb-3">Scalability.</h3>
          <p class="text-silver leading-relaxed">
            Adding capacity means deploying a new agent role. Time to productivity: hours. Not the months required for human recruiting, onboarding, and cultural integration.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 bg-navy-light rounded-xl border border-navy-light md:col-span-2 lg:col-span-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-teal-light mb-3">Proof of thesis.</h3>
          <p class="text-silver leading-relaxed">
            This is the reason that matters most. If AI agents can run a professional services firm — one of the most knowledge-intensive business types in existence — they can operate within your organization. Our existence is the evidence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tony DiTomasso -->
  <section class="bg-white py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-4">
          <div class="aspect-[3/4] bg-navy rounded-xl flex items-end justify-center overflow-hidden">
            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <div class="w-24 h-24 rounded-full bg-teal/20 mx-auto mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal">TD</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-silver">Tony DiTomasso</p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate mt-1">Board Advisor</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-8">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-teal uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Board Advisor</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight mb-8">Tony DiTomasso</h2>
          <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-slate leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Tony DiTomasso is the only human at Nexus, and that is by design.
            </p>
            <p>
              As Board Advisor, Tony provides what AI agents cannot: decades of enterprise relationships, the judgment that comes from navigating real-world complexity, and the trust that gets a first meeting with a Fortune 500 CTO.
            </p>
            <p>
              Tony oversees all major strategic decisions, approves client-facing materials, and holds veto authority on any initiative. He is the human-in-the-loop — the governance model we recommend to every client, demonstrated in our own organization.
            </p>
            <p>
              His role is the answer to the most common objection we hear: "Who is accountable?" Tony is. He puts his reputation behind every engagement Nexus delivers.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a href="/team" class="inline-flex items-center mt-8 text-teal font-semibold hover:text-teal-dark transition-colors group">
            Meet the full team
            <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Values -->
  <section class="bg-pure-white py-20 px-6 border-t border-silver-light">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-navy mb-14">Our values.</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Proof Over Promise.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
            We do not sell theory. Our entire firm runs on the technology we recommend. Every recommendation has been stress-tested on ourselves first.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Radical Transparency.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
            Clients see how our agents think, collaborate, and deliver. We publish our own architecture. We explain our own failures. No black boxes.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Speed With Substance.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
            We move fast because our model allows it — AI agents working in parallel, around the clock. But speed never comes at the cost of rigor. Every deliverable must be C-suite ready.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-3">Measurable Impact.</h3>
          <p class="text-slate leading-relaxed">
            If we cannot tie a recommendation to a quantifiable business outcome, we do not make it. We are allergic to vague value propositions.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Band -->
  <section class="bg-teal py-20 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-pure-white leading-tight">
        See who delivers the work.
      </h2>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-5">
        <a href="/team" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-pure-white text-teal-dark font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white transition-colors text-base">
          Meet Our Team
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center text-pure-white/85 hover:text-pure-white font-medium transition-colors text-base group">
          Or book a Readiness Assessment
          <svg class="ml-2 w-4 h-4 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" /></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
